reviews.author: Luke R
reviews.content:
Really lovely place to visit if you're staying in or driving through Kamala.

They have lovely drinks, including coffees, cold drinks and happy to offer water free of charge.

Great collection and quality of weed too, can buy pre-rolls or bud and they have gear to roll there which is super handy.
3 different floors all very nicely decorated with balconies you can chill at. If you're not smoking then it's still a great place to relax amongst some beautiful views.

The hosts were lovely and welcoming. There's games to play at the tables and plenty of room to get work done quietly if needed.

Great place to chill and watch the full moon from as you get a great view from the balcony.
